## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

Ensure you have the required tools installed:

```bash
iron doctor
```

### Development

{{- if eq .Project.Spec.DevEnvironment.Type "devcontainer" }}

1. Open this project in VS Code
2. When prompted, reopen in devcontainer
3. The devcontainer will set up all tools automatically
{{- end }}

{{- if .Computed.HasNode }}

Install dependencies:

```bash
{{ .Project.Spec.Monorepo.PackageManager }} install
```
{{- end }}

Start local development:

```bash
{{- if eq .Project.Spec.DevEnvironment.DevTool "tilt" }}
tilt up
{{- end }}
```

### Generate New Services

```bash
iron generate service my-service --type node-api --group my-group
iron generate service my-worker --type go-api --group workers
iron generate package my-lib --scope {{ .Computed.PrimaryScope }}
```

### Add Infrastructure Components

```bash
iron add redis
iron add kafka
iron add observability
```

## Project Structure

```
{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/
  apps/                    # Microservices
  packages/                # Shared libraries
{{- if .Computed.HasNode }}
    node/                  # Node.js packages
{{- end }}
{{- if .Computed.HasGo }}
    go/                    # Go packages
{{- end }}
  k8s/
    helm/
      {{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/  # Service Helm charts
      infra/               # Infrastructure charts
{{- if .Computed.HasArgoCD }}
    argocd/                # GitOps configuration
{{- end }}
  dockerfiles/             # Shared Dockerfiles
{{- if ne .Project.Spec.Cloud.Provider "none" }}
  iac/pulumi/              # Infrastructure as Code
{{- end }}
  utils/
    tilt/                  # Tilt utility files
  scripts/                 # Utility scripts
```

## Architecture

