- **Local K8s**: {{ .Project.Spec.DevEnvironment.K8sLocal }} cluster with {{ .Project.Spec.DevEnvironment.DevTool }} hot reload
- **Deployment**: Helm charts{{ if .Project.Spec.GitOps.Enabled }} + {{ .Project.Spec.GitOps.Tool }} GitOps{{ end }}
{{- if ne .Project.Spec.Cloud.Provider "none" }}
- **Cloud**: {{ .Project.Spec.Cloud.Provider | upperCase }} ({{ .Project.Spec.Cloud.Region }})
- **IaC**: Pulumi (TypeScript)
{{- end }}

